msgid "0:梨深ルート有り"
msgstr "0:梨深ルート有り"

msgid "100:梨深ルート無し"
msgstr "100:梨深ルート無し"

msgid "200:いつの間にか、いつもアニメエイトからベースへ帰るときに使う、円山町の狭い路地に立っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "200:At some point, I found myself on a narrow street in Maruyamacho. This was the route I used on my way back to the Base from animeight,[%p]"

msgid "300:まぶたを、何度かまたたかせてみる。[%p]"
msgstr "300:I forced myself to blink several times.[%p]"

msgid "400:カバンの中をのぞき込んでみた。[linebreak]教科書が数冊と、携帯ゲーム機が入っているだけ。[%p]"
msgstr "400:Then I took a look inside my bag. There were a few textbooks, along with a portable game system.[%p]"

msgid "500:今日は、アニメエイトではなにも買わなかった。[linebreak]いつもは必ずなにかひとつ買うようにしてるんだけど。[%p]"
msgstr "500:I hadn't bought anything at animeight today. Usually, I always made sure to buy at least one thing.[%p]"

msgid "600:僕はため息をついてから、歩を進め始めた。[linebreak]ここからベースまでは１５分もかからない。[%p]"
msgstr "600:I sighed and started to walk. From here, it was less than fifteen minutes to the Base.[%p]"

msgid "700:駅からちょっと離れるだけで道からは煌々とした照明やネオンは姿を消し、人の気配も少なくなる。[%p]"
msgstr "700:You didn't have to get that far from the station for all the lights and neon to disappear, along with most of the people.[%p]"

msgid "800:ホテル街へ向かう中年カップルや、この付近に家があるサラリーマンをたまに見かけるぐらいで、どちらかと言うと閑散とした雰囲気。[%p]"
msgstr "800:At most, you saw middle-aged couples heading for the hotels, or salarymen heading to their homes nearby. It was quiet and calm.[%p]"

msgid "900:ＤＱＮで溢れかえっていたセンター街と同じ渋谷だとはとても思えない。[%p]"
msgstr "900:It was hard to believe that this was the same Shibuya as Center Street, with its hordes of DQNs.[%p]"

msgid "1000:どうやら夜になって雲が出てきたらしくて、月は隠れてしまっていた。そのせいでいつもよりさらに道は暗かった。[%p]"
msgstr "1000:It was cloudy tonight, and the moon was hidden. The street seemed even darker than usual.[%p]"

msgid "1100:[name]拓巳[line]「……また、だ」[%p]"
msgstr "1100:[name]拓巳[line]Again...[%p]"

msgid "1200:見慣れた風景。薄汚い路地。[%p]"
msgstr "1200:I knew the route well, with its filthy, dark street.[%p]"

msgid "1300:それなのに、まるで異界にでも迷い込んでしまったかのような奇妙な感覚に襲われた。[%p]"
msgstr "1300:But today, it felt strange, like I'd wandered into another world.[%p]"

msgid "1400:風景そのものは変わっていないのに、初めてこの場所に足を踏み入れたような。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:Everything looked the same as always, but it felt like I was coming here for the first time.[%p]"

msgid "1500:それに、生ゴミの腐ったような匂いも漂ってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:And there was this odd smell, like rotting garbage.[%p]"

msgid "1600:肌にまとわりつくジメジメとした湿気は、雨が降ったんじゃないかって勘違いしそうなくらいだ。空気が粘ついている気がする。[%p]"
msgstr "1600:I could feel the humidity clinging to my skin. If I hadn't known better, I would've assumed it had just rained. The air felt... sticky.[%p]"

msgid "1700:[name]拓巳[line]「いや、ちょっと待った……」[%p]"
msgstr "1700:[name]拓巳[line]No, hang on.[%p]"

msgid "1800:――“また”って、いつのことだ？[%p]"
msgstr "1800:What did I mean “again”?[%p]"

msgid "1900:以前に[color index="A0FF0000"][ruby-base]未視感[ruby-text-start]ジャメヴュ[ruby-text-end][color index="800000"]を感じたのは、いつだった？[%p]"
msgstr "1900:I'd felt a sense of [color index="A0FF0000"]jamais vu[color index="800000"] before. When was it?[%p]"

msgid "2000:くそぅ、現実と妄想がごっちゃになってる。[linebreak]これじゃテレビのワイドショーに出てくる、うさんくさそうな専門家のステレオタイプな分析みたいじゃないか。[%p]"
msgstr "2000:Damn it. I was getting reality and my delusions mixed up. That was what the psychologists on TV said would happen if you played too many video games.[%p]"

msgid "2100:とにかく、未視感を今まさに感じているのは確かだった。[%p]"
msgstr "2100:Either way, it felt like I was coming here for the first time.[%p]"

msgid "2200:そして、[linebreak]それだけじゃなくて、[%p]"
msgstr "2200:And...[%p]"

msgid "2300:首筋が、チリチリとするあの感じ。[linebreak]誰かが僕を天から見下ろしている、あの感覚。[%p]"
msgstr "2300:That wasn't all. I felt a prickling on the back of my neck. A feeling like somebody was looking down at me.[%p]"

msgid "2400:錯覚なんかじゃない。どれだけ歩を速めたって、“視線”はどこまでも僕を追ってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "2400:I wasn't imagining it. No matter how fast I tried to walk, the gaze kept following me.[%p]"

msgid "2500:今、僕は絶対に誰かに見られている。それくらい強烈な気配を持つ“視線”だ。[%p]"
msgstr "2500:Somebody was watching me right now. Their gaze was so powerful I could physically feel it.[%p]"

msgid "2600:振り返りたい。[linebreak]でも、あえて振り返らない。[%p]"
msgstr "2600:I wanted to look back... But I decided not to.[%p]"

msgid "2700:これは、時々チャレンジしてみたくなるゲームだ。[%p]"
msgstr "2700:This was a game I sometimes played with myself.[%p]"

msgid "2800:なにか小さな物音がしたり、誰かに見られているような気がしても[%p]"
msgstr "2800:Whenever I heard a small sound, or felt like somebody was watching me,[%p]"

msgid "2900:“ちょっとやそっとじゃ振り向かないぞゲーム”。[%p]"
msgstr "2900:I'd play the “I'm Not Turning Around That Easy” game.[%p]"

msgid "3000:振り向いたら負けだ。[%p]"
msgstr "3000:If I turned around, I lost.[%p]"

msgid "3100:視線を感じるとだいたいいつも頭の中で妄想するのは、背後にすごくおっかない顔をした幽霊とかモンスターがいる……みたいな妄想。[%p]"
msgstr "3100:Usually, whenever I felt the gaze, I had delusions about ghosts or monsters with incredibly scary faces.[%p]"

msgid "3200:まあ、どっちにしてもこの１７年間、振り向いたってそこに実際になにかがいた試しはないし。[%p]"
msgstr "3200:Yet throughout all seventeen years of my life, I'd never turned around and actually seen something there.[%p]"

msgid "3300:ある程度の保険付きで、この脳内独り用ゲームを楽しむようになった。[%p]"
msgstr "3300:I'd kind of started to enjoy this game, since I knew I was probably safe.[%p]"

msgid "3400:それ風に耳を澄ましたり、片方の眉を上げて怪訝な顔をしてみたり、マンガっぽくセリフを言ってみたり。[%p]"
msgstr "3400:I'd listen for a moment, then raise an eyebrow in suspicion. Then I'd say a line from a manga.[%p]"

msgid "3500:別に、怖くて振り返らないわけじゃないんだからな。[%p]"
msgstr "3500:I-It wasn't that I was too scared to turn around, okay?[%p]"

msgid "3600:[name]拓巳[line]「き……き、貴様、見ているなっ」[%p]"
msgstr "3600:[name]拓巳[line]H-Hey... Y-you want a piece of me?[%p]"

msgid "3700:[name]拓巳[line]「その目だれの目？」[%p]"
msgstr "3700:[name]拓巳[line]Whose eyes are those?[%p]"

msgid "3800:[name]拓巳[line]「なんちゃって♪」[%p]"
msgstr "3800:[name]拓巳[line]Just kidding! ♪[%p]"

msgid "3900:自分自身へ必死に余裕っぷりをアピールしたつもりだった。[linebreak]でも、気が付けば僕は足を止めてしまっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "3900:I tried to desperately remind myself that I wasn't scared. But the next thing I knew, I'd stopped walking.[%p]"

msgid "4000:張り詰めたように感じる空気の中の、かすかな変化を感じて身がすくむ。いつの間にか顔は汗でぐっしょりと濡れ、膝が震えてよろけそうになる。[%p]"
msgstr "4000:I could feel the tension in the air change slightly. My face was damp with sweat, and my knees were threatening to buckle.[%p]"

msgid "4100:たまらず振り返ってみた。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:I gave in and turned around.[%p]"

msgid "4200:ゲームは負け。でも背後にはやっぱり誰もいない。車も通らない。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:I lost the game. But of course, there was nobody there. Not even a passing car.[%p]"

msgid "4300:なんだろう、この違和感は……[%p]"
msgstr "4300:Why did everything feel so strange all of a sudden?[%p]"

msgid "4400:[name]拓巳[line]「あ……」[%p]"
msgstr "4400:[name]拓巳[line]Oh...[%p]"

msgid "4500:耳鳴りがやんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "4500:The ringing in my ears had stopped.[%p]"

msgid "4600:音が止んでから気付いた。それまでずっと、耳鳴りのような音が聞こえていたことに。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:I only noticed after the sound stopped. Until that moment, there'd been a sound like a ringing in my ears.[%p]"

msgid "4700:それまでは鳴っていることをまったく認識してなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "4700:But I hadn't been aware of it at all.[%p]"

msgid "4800:そして、今度は、なにも聞こえなくなった。[linebreak]都会のど真ん中とは思えない、嘘のような突然の静けさ。[%p]"
msgstr "4800:Now, I couldn't hear anything. It was suddenly dead silent, far too silent for the middle of a city.[%p]"

msgid "4900:音が、すごくクリアに聞こえる気がする。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:It felt like any sound would be crystal clear.[%p]"

msgid "5000:僕はきつく目を閉じて、耳を澄ましてみた。[%p]"
msgstr "5000:I closed my eyes tight to listen.[%p]"

msgid "5100:やっぱり、なにも聞こえない。[%p]"
msgstr "5100:I couldn't hear anything.[%p]"

msgid "5200:変だ。[%p]"
msgstr "5200:This was weird.[%p]"

msgid "5300:変だよね……。[%p]"
msgstr "5300:This was weird, right?[%p]"

msgid "5400:普通だったら、遠くの方から電車が走る音だとか、車のクラクションの音だとか、そういうかすかな雑音がするはずなのに――。[%p]"
msgstr "5400:Usually, you could hear the sounds of distant trains, car horns, faint noise like that.[%p]"

msgid "5500:どうして……？[linebreak]僕の耳がおかしくなっちゃったのか？[%p]"
msgstr "5500:So why? Were my ears broken?[%p]"

msgid "5600:大声で叫び出したかった。そうしないと頭がおかしくなりそうな気がした。[%p]"
msgstr "5600:I wanted to scream as loud as I could. I felt like if I didn't, I'd go crazy.[%p]"

msgid "5700:でもできなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "5700:But I couldn't.[%p]"

msgid "5800:静かすぎて、この静寂を壊しちゃうような声を出したら大変なことになるんじゃないかっていう躊躇があった。[%p]"
msgstr "5800:It was so quiet, and it felt like if I broke the silence, something terrible would happen.[%p]"

msgid "5900:[name]拓巳[line]「……！」[%p]"
msgstr "5900:[name]拓巳[line]...![%p]"

msgid "6000:無音だった世界に、不意にひとつの音が入り込んできた。[%p]"
msgstr "6000:Suddenly, a single sound shattered the silent world.[%p]"

msgid "6100:ふと見ると、薄暗い道の先に沢山の“光るなにか”が落ちていた。アスファルト一面に撒き散らされている。[%p]"
msgstr "6100:I looked ahead and saw many shiny things lying on the dark ground. They were scattered all over the asphalt.[%p]"

msgid "6200:[name]拓巳[line]「……十字架？」[%p]"
msgstr "6200:[name]拓巳[line]Crosses?[%p]"

msgid "6300:それを認識した途端、さっきまでピクリとも動こうとしなかった僕の足が自然と前へ踏み出された。[%p]"
msgstr "6300:The moment I realized what they were, my legs unfroze and began to move forward.[%p]"

msgid "6400:散乱する十字架のひとつを拾い上げてみると、それは金属製で、長く伸びる先端は鋭い針のようになっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "6400:I picked one of them up. It was metal, and its long tip was sharp, like a needle.[%p]"

msgid "6500:――杭？\u3000それとも釘？[%p]"
msgstr "6500:A stake? A nail?[%p]"

msgid "6600:変な形をしているから、十字架と見間違えてしまった。[linebreak]そのまま、手にした杭を浮かされたような気分で握りしめた。[%p]"
msgstr "6600:It was strangely shaped, so I'd mistaken it for a cross. I gripped the stake, dazed.[%p]"

msgid "6700:聞こえる――。[linebreak]かすかに響いているなにかの音。[%p]"
msgstr "6700:I could hear it. A faint sound of some kind, echoing.[%p]"

msgid "6800:ゾクリと背筋を凍らせるような、冷たい音。[linebreak]それが断続的に聞こえてきている。[%p]"
msgstr "6800:A cold sound, one that would make your blood turn to ice. It would start, then stop, then start again.[%p]"

msgid "6900:僕の足は止まらない。その音のする方へと、意識が吸い寄せられていくかのように歩を進める。[%p]"
msgstr "6900:My legs kept moving forward. I walked on, as if drawn to the source of the sound.[%p]"

msgid "7000:怖いモノ見たさなのかな？[linebreak]それとも助けてほしいから？[linebreak]無音の世界から掬い上げてほしいから？[%p]"
msgstr "7000:Was it just a desire to see something scary? Maybe I wanted somebody to save me? To rescue me by plucking me out of this world of silence?[%p]"

msgid "7100:これじゃまるで、ドイツかどこかの民話みたいだ。[%p]"
msgstr "7100:It was like something from an old German fairytale.[%p]"

msgid "7200:あれはなんて言ったっけ……そう、ハーメルンの笛吹き男だ。その笛の音に誘われて行進する１００人以上の子供たち。[%p]"
msgstr "7200:Which one was it, again? Oh right. “The Pied Piper of Hamelin.” Where the piper leads over a hundred children on a march with the sound of his flute.[%p]"

msgid "7300:音は、やまない。[linebreak]なにかを打ち付けるイヤな音が、僕が進むごとにどんどん近づいてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "7300:The sound kept going. It was an awful sound, like something hitting something else. As I walked on it kept getting closer.[%p]"

msgid "7400:音は、左側にある細い路地の奥から聞こえてきた。[linebreak]この角を曲がれば、その音の正体が分かる。[%p]"
msgstr "7400:It was coming from the back of the narrow alley on the left. Once I rounded the corner, I'd see what it was.[%p]"

msgid "7500:なぜか引き返そうとは思わなかった。そんな考えすら浮かばなかった。[linebreak]僕を動かしているのが僕じゃないかのようだった。[%p]"
msgstr "7500:For some reason, I didn't think to turn around. The very idea of turning around never occurred to me. It was like I wasn't in control of my own body.[%p]"

msgid "7600:とにかく僕はその角を曲がり、[linebreak]そして目に飛び込んできたのは――[%p]"
msgstr "7600:I walked around the corner, and saw...[%p]"

msgid "7700:闇に浮かび上がる、[linebreak]鮮烈な、赤。[%p]"
msgstr "7700:In the darkness... Brilliant red.[%p]"

msgid "7800:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "7800:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "7900:最初に感じたのは“どこかで見たことのあるオブジェだなあ”っていう思いだった。[linebreak]それと“リアルに見えないな”ということ。[%p]"
msgstr "7900:The first thing I thought was that I'd seen something like it before. Also, that it didn't look real at all.[%p]"

msgid "8000:心のネジが何本か吹き飛んで感覚が麻痺しちゃったのかもしれない。いつもの僕だったら、恐怖のあまり情けない悲鳴を上げて腰を抜かし、その場で失禁していただろう。[%p]"
msgstr "8000:Maybe a few screws broke loose in my mind, and my senses had just become numb. In normal conditions, I would've screamed, fallen back on my butt, and peed myself right then and there.[%p]"

msgid "8100:ハリネズミか剣山みたいに、壁から無数に杭が突き出したオブジェ。そのオブジェをぼんやり眺めているうちに、杭の剣山から大量の赤い血が流れ出していることに気付いた。[%p]"
msgstr "8100:It was something that looked like a porcupine, or maybe a pincushion.. Countless stakes were nailed into the wall. As I stared at it, I realized that red blood was pouring out from beneath the stakes.[%p]"

msgid "8200:最初に見えた鮮烈な赤い色はこの血だまりだったんだ。[linebreak]表の路地の街路灯からかろうじて届く弱々しい光によって、[linebreak]その赤はしっとりとした光沢を放っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "8200:The brilliant red I'd seen was a pool of blood. Faint light from the street lamps outside the alley just barely reached in, making the red glisten.[%p]"

msgid "8300:さらに、なんだかよく分からないてらてらとした肉塊らしきものもいくつか転がっている。[%p]"
msgstr "8300:There were also all these little, glistening piles of... something. They kind of looked like hunks of meat.[%p]"

msgid "8400:息を呑もうとしたけど、のどがいつの間にかカラカラになっていて、唾液の一滴すら出なかった。[%p]"
msgstr "8400:I tried to swallow, but my throat was parched dry. There wasn't a single drop of saliva in my mouth.[%p]"

msgid "8500:僕は、気付いてしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "8500:I'd realized...[%p]"

msgid "8600:杭で打ち付けられているのは――[%p]"
msgstr "8600:The thing nailed to the wall by those stakes...[%p]"

msgid "8700:人間の、死体だ……。[%p]"
msgstr "8700:was a human corpse.[%p]"

msgid "8800:あまりにも常軌を逸していて。[linebreak]あまりにも容赦なくて。[linebreak]あまりにも徹底的で。[%p]"
msgstr "8800:This was so far removed from my everyday life... So brutal... So overwhelming.[%p]"

msgid "8900:そしてそれを為したのは、[linebreak]これだけの数の杭をコンクリートに打ち付けたのは、[%p]"
msgstr "8900:And the one who had done it... The one who'd pounded all these stakes into raw concrete...[%p]"

msgid "9000:たったひとりの、少女。[%p]"
msgstr "9000:was a single young girl.[%p]"

msgid "9100:なぜそう分かるのかと言えば――[%p]"
msgstr "9100:How could I tell?[%p]"

msgid "9200:真っ赤に塗れる手に杭の束を握りしめた少女が、まさに今、その“オブジェ”の前に、たたずんでいたから。[%p]"
msgstr "9200:Because she was standing right there in front of the corpse, holding stakes in her bloodstained hand.[%p]"

msgid "9300:僕から見ると彼女は背を向けている形になるから、いったいどんな顔をしているのかは確認できない。[%p]"
msgstr "9300:Her back was turned, so I couldn't tell what the look on her face was.[%p]"

msgid "9400:ただ、着ている制服は……翠明のものだった。[%p]"
msgstr "9400:But the uniform she was wearing... it was Suimei's.[%p]"

msgid "9500:さっきから感じていた、生ゴミの腐ったような匂いはますます強烈に僕の鼻をつき、断続的に吐き気が襲ってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "9500:The awful smell, like raw, rotting garbage, clung to my nostrils even more firmly. Every few seconds, I felt like I was about to throw up.[%p]"

msgid "9600:たまらず口元を押さえて、胃液が吹き出さないようにこらえた。[%p]"
msgstr "9600:I put my hand over my mouth so that I wouldn't vomit.[%p]"

msgid "9700:そこでようやく、さっき感じた“どこかで見たことのある”感覚――デジャヴの正体を思い出した。[%p]"
msgstr "9700:And then I finally realized where the sense of déjà vu I'd been having came from.[%p]"

msgid "9800:[name]拓巳[line]「あの時の……将軍の……リンク写真……！」[%p]"
msgstr "9800:[name]拓巳[line]The pictures in Shogun's links...[%p]"

msgid "9900:つい、声に出してしまった。それが、僕にとって致命的な行為だと気付かないままに。[%p]"
msgstr "9900:I didn't realize I'd spoken aloud until it was too late. This would prove to be a fatal mistake.[%p]"

msgid "10000:僕の声に、血に染まった“彼女”の肩が、ピクリと震えた。[%p]"
msgstr "10000:I saw the girl's shoulders twitch as she heard my voice.[%p]"

msgid "10100:そして、ゆっくりと僕の方を振り返る――[%p]"
msgstr "10100:Then she slowly turned around.[%p]"

msgid "10200:その視線が、僕を射抜く。[linebreak]なんて、仄暗い瞳……。[%p]"
msgstr "10200:Her gaze pierced me. Her eyes were so flat and empty...[%p]"

msgid "10300:彼女が――[linebreak]殺したんだ――[%p]"
msgstr "10300:She... had killed him…[%p]"

msgid "10400:“彼女”も、その音は聞いていた。[%p]"
msgstr "10400:She'd heard the sound, too.[%p]"

msgid "10500:最初は、ヒュンヒュンと空気を切り裂くような音だった。[linebreak]その音を発するバッグを持った、怪しい人影も見た。[linebreak]それを追いかけたが、逃げられてしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "10500:At first, it was a whooshing sound, like something slicing through the air. She had also seen the strange man who held the bag that made that sound. She'd chased him, but he'd gotten away.[%p]"

msgid "10600:その直後から、周囲に響き始めた。[linebreak]壁に杭を打ち付ける、甲高い音。[linebreak]ヒュンヒュンという音も、まだかすかに聞こえている。[%p]"
msgstr "10600:It was after that when she heard the echoing of the other sound. The loud, metallic sound of stakes being pounded into a wall. She could still hear the whooshing sound a little, too.[%p]"

msgid "10700:ふたつの音が共鳴して、耳が痛くなるかのような錯覚を覚える。[%p]"
msgstr "10700:The two sounds seemed to resonate, making her ears hurt.[%p]"

msgid "10800:[name]少女[line]「手遅れ、だった……？」[%p]"
msgstr "10800:[name]少女[line]I was too late?[%p]"

msgid "10900:軽く唇を噛み、彼女は音がする方へと走った。[linebreak]そこで見たものは――[%p]"
msgstr "10900:She bit her lip a little, then ran toward the source of the sound. What she saw there was...[%p]"

msgid "11000:壁に、十字架型の杭で張り付けにされた死体。[%p]"
msgstr "11000:A corpse, staked to the wall in the shape of a cross.[%p]"

msgid "11100:少女は焦りつつ、周囲を見回す。[%p]"
msgstr "11100:She panicked and looked around.[%p]"

msgid "11200:正直な話をすれば、この張り付けにされた被害者の生死は、彼女にはどうでもよかった。もちろん助けられたならそれに越したことはなかったが、それよりも優先すべきことがあった。[%p]"
msgstr "11200:In all honesty, she didn't care whether the victim on the wall was alive or dead. Of course, if they could be saved, that would be for the best, but it wasn't her highest priority.[%p]"

msgid "11300:ニシジョウタクミを、この場に近づけさせないこと。[linebreak]彼に、恐怖を与えないこと。[%p]"
msgstr "11300:Takumi Nishijo couldn't be allowed to get anywhere near here. She had to keep him from feeling afraid.[%p]"

msgid "11400:――彼は今、どこにいるだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "11400:Where was he?[%p]"

msgid "11500:そう考えながら、もう一度死体に目を戻す。[%p]"
msgstr "11500:She looked back at the body.[%p]"

msgid "11600:[name]少女[line]「……！」[%p]"
msgstr "11600:[name]少女[line]...![%p]"

msgid "11700:彼女は絶句していた。[%p]"
msgstr "11700:She couldn't believe her eyes.[%p]"

msgid "11800:目の前の死体が、ほんの数秒、目を離した隙に、無数の杭が全身に打ち付けられた凄惨なものへと変化していた。[%p]"
msgstr "11800:She'd only glanced away for a few seconds, but in that time, countless stakes had been embedded in the body.[%p]"

msgid "11900:確かに一瞬前まで、杭の数はほんの数本で、被害者の死体は血も流れずほぼ無傷だったはず。[%p]"
msgstr "11900:Only a moment ago, there had been only a few stakes. The body had been largely unharmed, with no signs of blood.[%p]"

msgid "12000:それが今、彼女の目の前で張り付けにされているのは、常軌を逸した惨状。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:But now, she was looking at something beyond belief.[%p]"

msgid "12100:彼女は愕然としつつ、必死で吐き気をこらえた。[linebreak]視界が、ぐにゃりと歪むような、不安定な感覚が襲う。[%p]"
msgstr "12100:Shocked, she struggled to keep from throwing up. Her vision went blurry as she began to tremble.[%p]"

msgid "12200:[name]少女[line]「妄想が、現実を侵食してる……？」[%p]"
msgstr "12200:[name]少女[line]The delusions are invading reality?[%p]"

msgid "12300:そこで、さらに新たな変化に、気付く。[%p]"
msgstr "12300:She realized that other things had changed, too.[%p]"

msgid "12400:自分の服装が、変化していた。[linebreak]見たこともない、どこかの高校のものと思われる制服。[linebreak]それを、自分が着ていた。[%p]"
msgstr "12400:Her clothes were different. She was wearing what seemed like some sort of high school uniform. She didn't recognize it at all.[%p]"

msgid "12500:しかも、全身は血に染まり。[linebreak]手には、十字の杭を持ち。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:Her whole body was covered in blood, and in her hand, she held cross-shaped stakes.[%p]"

msgid "12600:[name]少女[line]「う、そ……？\u3000これって……」[%p]"
msgstr "12600:[name]少女[line]No way... Is this...[%p]"

msgid "12700:[name]少女[line]「妄想が、シンクロを……！？」[%p]"
msgstr "12700:[name]少女[line]The delusions are synchronizing?[%p]"

msgid "12800:自分以外の誰かの妄想が、彼女の目に見えているものに変化を与えた。[%p]"
msgstr "12800:Someone else's delusions were affecting what she saw.[%p]"

msgid "12900:目の前の凄惨な死体、自分の服装、血の鮮烈な朱色。[linebreak]これらはすべて、現実？[%p]"
msgstr "12900:The brutal murder in front of her, her clothes, the brilliant red blood... Were these real?[%p]"

msgid "13000:[name]少女[line]「違う……」[%p]"
msgstr "13000:[name]少女[line]No...[%p]"

msgid "13100:それは現実ではなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "13100:They weren't.[%p]"

msgid "13200:血の匂いがしない。手に持っている杭に存在感も冷たい手触りもない。自分の頬にこびりついた血に、指で触れてみる。ドロリとした生ぬるい感触は――やはり、ない。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:The blood didn't smell like anything. The stakes in her hand had no weight, and didn't feel cold. She touched the blood on her forehead. Just like she thought, there was no wetness, no slick sensation.[%p]"

msgid "13300:目の前の死体に突き立てられた杭のひとつに、恐る恐る手を伸ばす。[linebreak]つかもうとして、だが彼女の手は空を切っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:Fearfully, she reached out towards one of the stakes pinning the body in front of her to the wall. She tried to grab it, but her hand merely passed through instead.[%p]"

msgid "13400:すべて妄想――[linebreak]あまりにも、強烈な――[%p]"
msgstr "13400:It was all just a delusion. An incredibly powerful delusion...[%p]"

msgid "13500:この妄想がいつ現実になるかもしれない。[linebreak]すでに“妄想は為されてしまった”。[linebreak]後はリアルブートすれば、妄想は現実になる。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:A delusion that could become real. It had already been created. All that was left was to real-boot it, and it would become reality.[%p]"

msgid "13600:どうしよう、と彼女は不安になる。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:She felt worried. What should she do now?[%p]"

msgid "13700:これほど強力な負の妄想のテリトリー内に入ったのは、初めてだった。もしかしたら、ニシジョウタクミはこの超誇大妄想の使い手によって、もう殺されてしまっているかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "13700:She'd never been inside the territory of such a strong negative delusion. The Gigalomaniac responsible may have already killed Takumi Nishijo.[%p]"

msgid "13800:あるいは、目の前で張り付けにされている遺体が、いつニシジョウタクミの遺体に変化してもおかしくない。[%p]"
msgstr "13800:The body in front of her could transform into him at any moment.[%p]"

msgid "13900:彼女は、焦りのあまりうめき声を漏らし、その直後に――[%p]"
msgstr "13900:She let out a soft, panicked cry, and then...[%p]"

msgid "14000:[name]拓巳[line]「あの時の……将軍の……リンク写真……！」[%p]"
msgstr "14000:[name]拓巳[line]The pictures in Shogun's links...[%p]"

msgid "14100:背後からの、怯えた少年の声を聞いた。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:She heard the voice of a frightened boy behind her.[%p]"

msgid "14200:[name]少女[line]「あ……」[%p]"
msgstr "14200:[name]少女[line]Oh...[%p]"

msgid "14300:意表を突かれたように、僕を見て目を丸くした“彼女”は、すぐに泣き笑いのような表情になって、絞り出すように――[%p]"
msgstr "14300:She looked at me with startled, wide eyes. Her expression then shifted to something that combined a smile with tears. And then…[%p]"

msgid "14400:[name]少女[line]「よか……った……」[%p]"
msgstr "14400:[name]少女[line]I'm so glad…[%p]"

msgid "14500:そう、つぶやいた。[%p]"
msgstr "14500:She whispered.[%p]"

msgid "14600:よかった？[linebreak]なにが、よかったんだ？[%p]"
msgstr "14600:Glad? Glad about what?[%p]"

msgid "14700:そもそも、なんでこの状況で、僕を見て笑うんだ？[%p]"
msgstr "14700:Why would anybody be glad about anything right now?[%p]"

msgid "14800:意味不明だった。意味不明すぎて、背筋を冷たいものが走り、僕は慌てて目をそらす。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:It didn't make sense. It was so bizarre I felt a cold chill run down my spine, and quickly looked away.[%p]"

msgid "14900:反射的に“妙なことに巻き込まれたくない”って考えた。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:It suddenly occurred to me that I didn't want to get involved in anything weird.[%p]"

msgid "15000:僕はリアル女とは目を見て話せないし、それどころか彼女は紛れもない殺人鬼だ。もうすぐ警察も来るだろうし、それにお腹もすいた……。[%p]"
msgstr "15000:I couldn't talk to real girls, anyway. Also, she was a murderer. The cops were on their way. I was hungry, too.[%p]"

msgid "15100:そうだ、だから帰ろう。[linebreak]今すぐこの場から立ち去ろう。でないと僕は……[%p]"
msgstr "15100:Yeah, time to go home. Time to leave. Otherwise, I'd...[%p]"

msgid "15200:狂ってしまう――[%p]"
msgstr "15200:I'd go crazy.[%p]"

msgid "15300:[name]少女[line]「タク……」[%p]"
msgstr "15300:[name]少女[line]Taku...[%p]"

msgid "15400:[name]拓巳[line]「っ！？」[%p]"
msgstr "15400:[name]拓巳[line]?![%p]"

msgid "15500:唐突に“彼女”が僕の名を呼んだ。[linebreak]僕は名乗ってない。彼女と会うのは初めてなのに。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:Suddenly, she said my name. I hadn't introduced myself. I'd never even seen her before.[%p]"

msgid "15600:[name]少女[line]「あなたに、会いたかった」[%p]"
msgstr "15600:[name]少女[line]I wanted to meet you.[%p]"

msgid "15700:僕を見る彼女の唇が、恐ろしいほどに不敵な形に歪む。[linebreak]まるで悪魔のように――[%p]"
msgstr "15700:Her lips curled upward into a terrible grin. Like a demon's...[%p]"

msgid "15800:僕は悲鳴を上げていた。[linebreak]そうしながら、がむしゃらに走り出していた。[linebreak]息が苦しくなっても叫び続け、とにかく必死で走り続けた。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:I screamed. And as I screamed, I ran. I kept yelling until my throat hurt, running as fast as I could.[%p]"

msgid "15900:一度だけ背後を振り向いたけど、“彼女”が追ってくることはなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:Just once, I looked back, but she wasn't following me.[%p]"

